			<title>智慧財產權與自由軟體應用</title>
			<link>https://www.openfoundry.org/en/activities/details/190</link>
			<guid>https://www.openfoundry.org/en/activities/details/190</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[Title: 智慧財產權與自由軟體應用<br />Venue: [台南] 南榮技術學院 / 台南市<br />Category: Campus Speech<br />Date: 2011.11.16<br />Time: 13:00  - 17:00 <br />Description: <div class="media">
<div class="typo-icon"><strong>感謝各界先進的參與，本活動已圓滿結束，如有任何問題歡迎跟活動聯絡人連繫。<br /></strong><strong><a href="https://www.openfoundry.org/tw/foss-promotion-on-campus/cat_view/58-/570-2011-/638-1116" target="_blank">簡報檔案</a></strong></div>
